+# CLI TUI Architecture - Model Label Display
+
+## Single Source of Truth for Current Model
+
+### Problem
+Previously, there was no unified way to determine "what model is currently active" in the UI.
+- Each message had its own `modelLabel`
+- No consistent display of the current model in the status/header area
+- Potential for confusion when the model changes between messages
+
+### Solution
+The `App` component now maintains `displayModel` state as the single source of truth for the currently active model.
